import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { FormBuilder, FormGroup, Validator, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; import { OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Reservation } from '../model/reservation'; import { ReservationService } from '../reservation/reservation.service'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-reservation-form', templateUrl: './reservation-form.component.html', styleUrls: ['./reservation-form.component.css'], }) export class ReservationFormComponent implements OnInit { reservationForm: FormGroup = new FormGroup({}); constructor( private formBuilder: FormBuilder, private reservationService: ReservationService, private router: Router, private activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute ) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.reservationForm = this.formBuilder.group({ checkInDate: ['', Validators.required], checkOutDate: ['', Validators.required], guestName: ['', Validators.required], guestEmail: ['', [Validators.required, Validators.email]], roomNumber: ['', Validators.required], }); let id = this.activatedRoute.snapshot.paramMap.get('id'); if (id) { let reservation = this.reservationService.getReservation(id); if (reservation) { this.reservationForm.patchValue(reservation); } } } onSubmit() { if (this.reservationForm.valid) { let reservation: Reservation = this.reservationForm.value; let id = this.activatedRoute.snapshot.paramMap.get('id'); if (id) { // update: this.reservationService.updateReservation(id,reservation); } else { // new: this.reservationService.addReservation(reservation); } this.router.navigate(['/list']); } } }
